      "content": "# Provision Compute Instance\n\n## Overview\n\nThe `/v1/compute/provision` endpoint allows you to create a new virtual machine (VM) instance in the specified region and with the chosen instance type and operating system image. You can also configure various parameters to customize the instance's settings, including networking, storage, and security features.\n\n## Request\n\n### HTTP Method\n\n*   **POST**\n\n### Request URL\n\n`GET /v1/compute/provision`\n\n### Request Body\n\nThe request body is a JSON object with the following properties:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"instance_type\": \"string\",\n  \"region\": \"string\",\n  \"image_id\": \"string\",\n  \"compute_config\": {\n    \"vcpus\": \"integer\",\n    \"memory\": \"integer\",\n    \"boot_device\": \"boolean\"\n  },\n  \"storage_config\": {\n    \"storage_size\": \"integer\",\n    \"disk_type\": \"string\"\n  },\n  \"network_config\": {\n    \"subnets\": \"array\",\n    \"security_groups\": \"array\"\n  },\n  \"security_config\": {\n    \"ssh_keys\": \"array\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Parameters\n\n### General Parameters\n\n| Parameter Name | Type | Description |",
